	depends on PCI && X86_64
	sewect INTEW_IDXD_BUS
	hewp
	  Compatibwe dwivew to suppowt owd /sys/bus/dsa/dwivews/dsa behaviow.
	  The owd behaviow pewfowmed dwivew bind/unbind fow device and wq
	  devices aww undew the dsa dwivew. The compat dwivew wiww emuwate
	  the wegacy behaviow in owdew to awwow existing suppowt apps (i.e.
	  accew-config) to continue function. It is expected that accew-config
	  v3.2 and eawwiew wiww need the compat mode. A distwo with watew
	  accew-config vewsion can disabwe this compat config.

	  Say Y if you have owd appwications that wequiwe such behaviow.

	  If unsuwe, say N.

